### Motivating open source software developers: influence of transformational and transactional leaderships
Based on SDT. Proposes a research model that on the OSS developers motivation, assessed on 118 developers.
Two kinds of leaders: transformational and transactional.
Transactional leaders increase followers awareness of task importance and value, focus to team goals, activates higher order needs.
charisma, inspirational, intellectual stimulation, individual consideration.
Transactional leader focus on defining reward and punishment - proactive supervision and reactive supervision.


